https://btrfs.wiki.kernel.org/index.php/Btrfs%28command%29

Raid 1:
#Use raid1 for both data and metadata
mkfs.btrfs -L label -m raid1 -d raid1 /dev/sdb /dev/sdc

See subvolumes:
sudo btrfs subvolume list -atu /

Get UID of blocks:
$ blkid
